data.description: Welcome to your own slice of paradise!  1.59-acre lot, this manufactured home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, & privacy. 1344 sqft of living space. As you enter through the gated entry your long driveway will make you appreciate the sense of security & exclusivity that this property provides. Step inside & be greeted by the warm & inviting ambiance of the open-concept living area. Natural light & the skylight illuminates the atmosphere. Whether you're entertaining guests or simply relaxing with family, this versatile layout is perfect for everyday living. Retreat to the spacious master suite, complete w/a private ensuite bath & plenty of closet space for all your storage needs. The expansive 1.59-acre lot provides plenty of space for outdoor recreation, gardening, or simply enjoying the beauty of nature. A shop adds extra convenience & storage for your tools, equipment, or hobbies. Don't miss your chance to make this charming manufactured home yours.
